“DO NOT TRUST THIS HOTEL”


Reviewed July 11, 2014




After booking a room for a four day weekend in Portland, I arrived and they had canceled my reservation. Trying to say that I canceled the reservation (which I definitely did not) they were extremely rude. Probably for the best as the lobby had a stench and was certainly not clean. Never ever.





Stayed July 2014, traveled on business





