PdxValueInns, Guest Relations Manager at Downtown Value Inn, responded to this review,
July 25, 2014


We appreciate hearing from you about your stay with us at the Downtown Value Inn. Feedback from our guests, both positive and negative, is an important tool for us to improve our hospitality in every way we can. We apologize that the service you received was unsatisfactory. Discourtesy is unprofessional and unacceptable. We were happy to hear that you were pleased with the quality of your room on the third floor. We would welcome the opportunity to hear more from you about your experience. We can be contacted at guestrelations@downtownvalueinn.com. We certainly hope that whether you choose to stay with us again or with someone else that you will return often to the Rose City in the future.



Report response as inappropriate

