PdxValueInns, Guest Relations Manager at Downtown Value Inn, responded to this review,
July 27, 2014


Thank you for posting your review here on TripAdvisor. The opinions of our guests are very important to us. We were disappointed to hear about the troubles you encountered during your stay with us. We apologize that you had such a long wait to check in, and that the facilities did not meet your expectations. Especially things as fundamental as the shower and the hot water. Was the front desk staff unable to provide a different room when asked? Of course if the property was fully booked that day it might not have been possible. We try to respond to issues with the rooms as soon as possible in order to ensure our patrons are comfortable. We would like very much to hear more from you about your time with us at the Downtown Value Inn. We can be reached at guestrelations@downtownvalueinn.com.



Report response as inappropriate

Thank you. We appreciate your input.


This response is the subjective opinion of the management representative and not of TripAdvisor LLC.




















M P



Victoria, British Columbia





